$Id$

1. 	How can I run this project?
	Download javascript v8 nodejs project at http://nodejs.org/dist/node-v0.1.98.tar.gz
	Unpack the tar ball: tar -zxvf node-v0.1.98.tar.gz
	And run: ./configure && make && make install
	Or if you prefer, visit http://nodejs.org/#download for more information.
	Completing this steps, you can run ircd.js: sh$ node ircd.js

2. 	What IRC Client can I use to connect to openircd ?
	Actually IRC Clients supported: mIRC, X-Chat, KvIRC and irssi.

Help us coding, translating and otimizing this source project.

Thanks.